HiddenObjectGames.name: Farm Mysteries
HiddenObjectGames.description: Find all the hidden objects at the Farm. Click to find an object or difference.

HiddenObjectGames.name: Rome Hidden Objects
HiddenObjectGames.description: Find all the hidden objects in Rome. Click on all the hidden objects.

HiddenObjectGames.name: Fantasy - Hidden Stars
HiddenObjectGames.description: Find all the hidden stars on the fantasy images. Click on the spot where you found a star.

HiddenObjectGames.name: Funfair Mysteries
HiddenObjectGames.description: Find all the hidden objects at the Funfair. Click to find an object or difference.

HiddenObjectGames.name: Tokyo Hidden Objects
HiddenObjectGames.description: Find all the hidden objects in Tokyo. Click on all the hidden objects.

Skill.name: Traffic Control
Skill.description: Control traffic safely. Click on traffic lights to operate them.

Skill.name: Speed Directions
Skill.description: Complete the course. Click to change direction.

Skill.name: Red and Green 2
Skill.description: Shoot cannon balls and bump the creatures to their own sweets. Move to aim and click to shoot.

Skill.name: Happy Bird
Skill.description: Fly around and grab all items. Click on a rock and hold on to move up.

Skill.name: Red and Green
Skill.description: Shoot cannon balls and move the animals to their own sweets. Move to aim and click to shoot.

TripeaksGolf.name: Easter Island Solitaire
TripeaksGolf.description: Play a Tri-peaks game on Easter Island. Try to remove all cards by selecting cards that are 1 higher or 1 lower in value than the open card.

TripeaksGolf.name: Pyramid Tripeaks
TripeaksGolf.description: Fun Tripeaks Solitaire game in Ancient Egypt. Remove all cards by playing cards that are 1 higher or 1 lower in value then the open card.

TripeaksGolf.name: Santa Tripeaks
TripeaksGolf.description: Tripeaks Solitaire game for Christmas. Try to remove all cards by selecting cards that are 1 higher or lower in value than the open card at the bottom.

TripeaksGolf.name: Tri Towers Solitaire
TripeaksGolf.description: Remove all cards and reveal the three towers. You can remove cards from the game by clicking on cards that are 1 higher or 1 lower in value than the open card at the bottom. Click on the closed stack to get a new open card.

TripeaksGolf.name: Solitaire Harvest
TripeaksGolf.description: Remove all cards from this Golf Solitaire game. You can remove cards that are 1 higher or 1 lower in value than the open card. Click on the closed stack to get a new open card or use the jokers.

BrainGames.name: Harbour Escape
BrainGames.description: Escape from the harbour. Use logic to get your red boat out of the harbor. Move boats so your red boat can reach the exit.

BrainGames.name: Peg Solitaire
BrainGames.description: Remove all the Pegs but one by jumping over Pegs.

BrainGames.name: The Brain Train
BrainGames.description: Solve the train puzzles. Make sure the train can get out. Combine 3 of the same cars to remove them.

BrainGames.name: Neon Lights
BrainGames.description: Connect all the lamps to the main Battery. Click on a wire to rotate it.

BrainGames.name: BBQ Roast
BrainGames.description: Roast and grow food on the BBQ. Combine 3 or more of the same food to let it grow.

MahjongSolitaire.name: Black and White Mahjong 3
MahjongSolitaire.description: New Black and White Mahjong game. Combine a black tile and a white tile. You can only combine free tiles and tiles with the same symbols. Via level select you can play all 300 levels.

MahjongSolitaire.name: Music Mahjong
MahjongSolitaire.description: A mahjong solitaire game full of music. Remove tiles in pairs of the same free tiles. Try to free the tiles with the music notes.

MahjongSolitaire.name: Dream Pet Solitaire
MahjongSolitaire.description: Play Solitaire Mahjong with the dream Pets. Combine 2 of the same pets to remove the pets.

MahjongSolitaire.name: Jewels Kyodai
MahjongSolitaire.description: Mahjong Solitaire with Jewels. Remove all tiles in pairs of the same free tiles.

MahjongSolitaire.name: Mahjong Solitaire
MahjongSolitaire.description: A Mahjong Solitaire game. Match 2 of the same free tiles to remove the tiles.

Puzzles.name: Shape Grid
Puzzles.description: Move shapes on the grid. Groups of 4 or more of the same tiles are removed.

Puzzles.name: Block Monsters 1010 Extreme
Puzzles.description: Drag the shapes on the playing area and complete rows and/or columns. Click a shape to rotate it.

Puzzles.name: Trump Sweeper
Puzzles.description: Try to find all trumps in this minesweeper game.

Puzzles.name: Block Monsters 1010
Puzzles.description: Drag the shapes on the playing area and complete rows and/or columns.

Puzzles.name: Extreme Vexed
Puzzles.description: Your goal is to move similar blocks together to remove those blocks. Remove all blocks to advance to the next level. Drag blocks to an empty spot to move them.

Match3Games.name: Flower World 2
Match3Games.description: New levels for Flower World: match 3 game. Swap 2 flowers and match 3 or more in a row. Reach the indicated goals.

Match3Games.name: Emoji Match 3
Match3Games.description: Match 3 game with Emoji's. Swap 2 emoji's to get 3 or more on a row. Remove the special backgrounds.

Match3Games.name: Princess Jewels
Match3Games.description: Match3 game with the Jewels of the Princess.  Drop blocks down and combine 3 same jewels horizontally, vertically or diagonally. Change the order of the jewels with the arrow keys.

Match3Games.name: Circus Match 3
Match3Games.description: Play a match 3 game in the Circus. Swap 2 items to get 3 or more in a row. Remove all colored backgrounds.

Match3Games.name: Aladdin and the Magic Lamp
Match3Games.description: Collect the magic items. Let the items drop down to collect them. Click on a spot that when swapped with a neighbouring tile would match 3 or more in a row.

Shooting.name: Archery Training
Shooting.description: Train your shooting skills. Aim, shoot and hit the bulls eye.

Shooting.name: Airport Sniper
Shooting.description: Shoot the targets at the airport. Click to zoom in and then aim and release.

Shooting.name: Galaxy Shooter
Shooting.description: Bescherm de aarde tegen de buitenaardse ruimteschepen. Tap/click to shoot.

Shooting.name: Archer
Shooting.description: Shoot carefully and hit only the fruit. Click and drag to aim and release to shoot.

Shooting.name: Soldier Attack 3
Shooting.description: Extra levels: hit the aliens in as less shots as possible. Aim and click to shoot.

Pinball.name: Pinball Breakout
Pinball.description: What do you get if you combine Pinball and Breakout? Shoot all the bricks using the pinball flippers.

Pinball.name: Neon Pinball
Pinball.description: Neon Pinball game. Use the arrow keys to control the game or drag and tap on the screen.

Pinball.name: Pinball
Pinball.description: Classic Pinball game. Use the arrow keys to control the game or drag and tap on the screen.

MahjongGames.name: Triple Tiles
MahjongGames.description: Combine three of the same tiles. Remove all tiles to advance to the next level.

MahjongGames.name: Olko 2
MahjongGames.description: Remove all tiles from the game. You can only reach the tiles via the sides.

MahjongGames.name: Time Mahjong
MahjongGames.description: Mahjong game with special time tiles. Remove all tiles in pairs of the same free tiles. Remove two free time tiles for extra time.

MahjongGames.name: Zoo Mahjong
MahjongGames.description: Combine three of the same Mahjong tiles in Japan. Remove all stones to advance to the next level.

MahjongGames.name: Pyramid Mahjong Solitaire
MahjongGames.description: A Pyramid Solitaire game with Mahjong Tiles. Choose 1 or 2 tiles up to a total value of 13. An A=1, a J=11, a Q=12 and a K is 13.

Board.name: Block Domino
Board.description: Classic block domino game. Try to play your tiles on the table before your opponent does.

Board.name: All Threes Domino
Board.description: Play All Threes Domino game with your partner. Drag tiles on the board, try to get multiples of 3 on the ends of the domino chain to score.

Board.name: All Fives Domino
Board.description: Play all Fives Domino game with your partner. Drag tiles on the board, try to get multiples of 5 on the ends of the domino chain to score.

Board.name: Bingo
Board.description: The ultimate Bingo game. Mark the balls on your bingo cards and click 'Bingo' when you have 5 in a row.

Board.name: The Royal Game of Ur
Board.description: Play the board game The Royal Game of Ur. Throw the dice and race to the end and be the first to get all your stones over the finish.

TowerDefense.name: Tesla Defense
TowerDefense.description: Defend your base. Shoot at all enemies. You can build defenses to help you.

Arkanoid.name: Neon Breaker
Arkanoid.description: Shoot all the bricks. Aim and release to shoot.

Arkanoid.name: Neon Arkanoid
Arkanoid.description: Fun Arkanoid game in Neon Style. Use the paddle to bounce the ball and remove all neon bricks.

Arkanoid.name: Endless Break Out
Arkanoid.description: Remove the bricks in this endless Break Out Game. Bounce the ball with the paddle and try stay alive.

Arkanoid.name: Outer Space Arkanoid
Arkanoid.description: Classic Arkanoid or Breakout game in HTML5. Shoot all bricks with the ball and keep the ball in play with your paddle. Move the paddle with the mouse or with your finger on Mobile devices.

Sports.name: Dunk Balls
Sports.description: Try to dunk all balls. Move the paddle and get the balls in the basket.

Sports.name: Ski Slalom
Sports.description: Ski Slalom winter game. Move left and right to turn and ski between the 2 gates everytime. Turning decreases your speed.

Sports.name: Basketball Legend
Sports.description: Fun basketball game. Shoot the ball in the basket. Drag on the screen to determine your shot.

Sports.name: Giant Slalom
Sports.description: Giant Slalom winter game. Move left and right and ski right of the red gate and left of the blue gate.

Sports.name: Downhill Ski
Sports.description: Downhill ski winter game. Move left and right and avoid all obstacles.

Retro.name: Coloring Mandalas
Retro.description: Coloring game with Mandalas. Select a mandala and start coloring. Save or print the result as an image.

Retro.name: Snow Balls
Retro.description: Catch all the snow balls. Use the arrow keys or tap the arrows on your screen.

Retro.name: Coloring for Kids
Retro.description: Fun Coloring game for kids. Select a drawing and start coloring. Save or print your work.

Retro.name: Alien Invaders 2
Retro.description: Shoot the aliens and save the planet. Drag your space ship and shoot the aliens.

Retro.name: Bubble Trouble
Retro.description: Destroy the all the bubbles. Shoot and destroy the bubbles. Use the arrow keys to move and the space bar to shoot. Or drag your character and tap to shoot.

Billiards.name: Carrom Pool
Billiards.description: Disc Pool game against a computer opponent. Pocket all your discs in one of the four corners. If you pocked the red disc, you must pocked one of your discs in the next shot.

Billiards.name: Bubble Ball
Billiards.description: Try to shoot all bubbles in the central hole. Drag the shooter bubble to shoot.

Billiards.name: Neon Billiards
Billiards.description: Single player Pool Billiards game. Pocket all the balls and the 8 ball as last ball. If you pocket the balls from low to high you get bonus points.

Billiards.name: Neon Ball
Billiards.description: Shoot all the neon balls from your opponent off the table. Drag your balls to determine strengh and direction of your shot.

Billiards.name: Trick Ball
Billiards.description: Remove all balls from the table by colliding the same balls.

Platform.name: Avoider
Platform.description: Jump up and avoid the platforms. Tap or use the space bar to jump.

Platform.name: Stay in the Dark
Platform.description: Stay in the dark and kill all the lights. Move around and hit the lights before you are exposed.

Platform.name: Catch the Thief
Platform.description: Catch all the Thieves by freezing them. Use the on-screen controls or the arrow keys and space bar.

Platform.name: Frozen for Christmas
Platform.description: Santa has to freeze all the Elves for Christmas. Use the on-screen controls or the arrow keys and space bar. Freeze and catch all the Elves.

Platform.name: Rainforest Jump
Platform.description: Move and jump in the rainforest and do not get crushed.

Snake.name: Neon Nibblet
Snake.description: Eat all the blue stars in the Snake-like game, but do not bit your own tail. Use the arrow keys or swipe on the screen.

Snake.name: Greedy Worm
Snake.description: Eat as many presents as you can. Click or Tap to let your worm change directions.

Snake.name: Classic Snake
Snake.description: Collect all the dots and avoid bumping into the wall or your tail.

PacMaze.name: Ms Tapman
PacMaze.description: Classic Ms. Pacman game. Eat all the yellow dots and avoid the ghosts.

PacMaze.name: SnowMan
PacMaze.description: Pacman in the Snow: SnowMan. Eat all the yellow dots and avoid the ghosts. Eat the big dots to be able to defeat the ghosts.

PacMaze.name: Classic Pac
PacMaze.description: Classic Pacman: eat all the yellow dots and avoid the ghosts.

PacMaze.name: Cookie Monster
PacMaze.description: Cookie Monster as Pacman. Eat all the pink dots and avoid the ghosts.

PacMaze.name: Tapman
PacMaze.description: Classic Pacman game. Eat all the yellow dots and avoid the ghosts.
